âœ… Summary

Philippines OS is a secure, trial-enabled OS for Arduino devices

Tied to a single Arduino account

Includes EEPROM storage, trial key system, server activation, SD card OS modules

Fully offline once activated

Designed for Philippine teenage users / tech enthusiasts
